"Creature — Human Wizard Sorcerer", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/2/f/2fe9e325-fbe4-4f43-8d68-8525c4d5ce8b.jpg?1782708313", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/2/f/2fe9e325-fbe4-4f43-8d68-8525c4d5ce8b.jpg?1782708313", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/m20/114/sorcerer-of-the-fang?utm_source=api", "local": "img/sorcerer/c1d5a631-a963-43a4-a5c0-1ba23bd88d0f.jpg"}, {"id": "20370c3b-231f-4d9d-8b6e-f1eb25fa4b5d", "name": "Sorcerous Sight", "set": "POR", "type_line": "Sorcery", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/e/c/ecfd43dc-e5fd-43bc-babb-fe7ecb6ccd00.jpg?1782755595", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/e/c/ecfd43dc-e5fd-43bc-babb-fe7ecb6ccd00.jpg?1782755595", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/por/68/sorcerous-sight?utm_source=api", "local": "img/sorcerer/20370c3b-231f-4d9d-8b6e-f1eb25fa4b5d.jpg"}, {"id": "6f858405-dfe4-4ca2-b2e3-80ce8cda5522", "name": "Vulshok Sorcerer", "set": "DDI", "type_line": "Creature — Human Shaman Sorcerer", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["R"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/b/7/b7153854-c548-48de-b9e2-72b7d9397563.jpg?1782752369", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/b/7/b7153854-c548-48de-b9e2-72b7d9397563.jpg?1782752369", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/ddi/50/vulshok-sorcerer?utm_source=api", "local": "img/sorcerer/6f858405-dfe4-4ca2-b2e3-80ce8cda5522.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Krovikan Sorcerer", "set": "VMA", "html": "&quot;These <mark>sorcerers</mark> always seem to have another surprise up their sleeves.&quot;\n—Zur the Enchanter", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/2/62909d11-9d2f-42a7-9b73-6b494bbe3f9e.jpg?1782751443"}, {"card": "Mystic Decree", "set": "ME4", "html": "&quot;Curse Reveka, and curse her coddled conjurers. Their <mark>sorcerers</mark>&#x27; school shall yet be ours.&quot;\n—Irini Sengir", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/b/2bc4a9a8-1c00-4e37-9942-3c7bb7ff8307.jpg?1782752753"}, {"card": "Wandering Stream", "set": "INV", "html": "&quot;Dominaria touches us all.&quot;\n—Molimo, maro-<mark>sorcerer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/d/6da5cb6c-253b-44f0-98f9-d75f42c6e14b.jpg?1782719993"}, {"card": "Bind", "set": "INV", "html": "&quot;The battlefield is cluttered enough. Be still.&quot;\n—Multani, maro-<mark>sorcerer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/f/cfa51783-9ef8-4e51-ba0d-ce8439d83bdf.jpg?1782720010"}, {"card": "Glint", "set": "DTK", "html": "Rakshasa waste no opportunity to display their wealth and power, even in the midst of a <mark>sorcerous</mark> duel.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/5/35fa105f-c76b-4fd0-9b83-34b46648e0d6.jpg?1782712753"}, {"card": "Sunastian Falconer", "set": "ME3", "html": "Sunastian has roots in both <mark>sorcery</mark> and swordplay; he has learned never to depend too heavily on the latter.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/d/bd0eb8b1-e48d-4e83-86df-d6aa86f95ffd.jpg?1782753310"}, {"card": "Flaring Flame-Kin", "set": "CNS", "html": "A flame-kin is always formidable, but feeding its fire with a <mark>sorcerous</mark> gift grants it the power to devastate armies.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/c/cc7aa01f-c647-43d2-8c4a-b93a198d03b4.jpg?1782713294"}, {"card": "Arcane Flight", "set": "DOM", "html": "The Tolarian Academies are known for their magical research, powerful <mark>sorcerers</mark>, and accidental destruction of ecosystems.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/9/09fbb1c0-ba57-4a5a-8ad6-77fbc6aeeec9.jpg?1782710166"}, {"card": "Ultimecia, Temporal Threat", "set": "FIN", "html": "&quot;Ultimecia is a fearful <mark>sorceress</mark>. Her heart is filled with anger and hate.&quot;\n—Edea Kramer", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/6/b64e4475-f1c6-4d85-b42f-6d84d06855bb.jpg?1782686126"}, {"card": "Vulshok Sorcerer", "set": "DDI", "html": "Vulshok <mark>sorcerers</mark> train by leaping into electrified storm clouds. Dead or alive, they come back down with smiles on their faces.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/7/b7153854-c548-48de-b9e2-72b7d9397563.jpg?1782752369"}, {"card": "Gravity Sphere", "set": "LEG", "html": "On the morning of the Battle of Gal-Shan, the <mark>Sorcerer</mark>&#x27;s cry rang out: &quot;Let no bird fly, let no creature take wing, let all the battle join as one.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/2/a2749332-e99a-4a0c-b3a3-5578b552fa11.jpg?1782722315"}, {"card": "Hurricane", "set": "10E", "html": "&quot;Don&#x27;t envy the grandeur of drakes. Their impression of grace fades when the first gust sends them crashing into one another.&quot;\n—Molimo, maro-<mark>sorcerer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/7/371d83e8-f514-433c-bc6a-e0eeef3fab2a.jpg?1782716474"}, {"card": "Shambling Goblin", "set": "JMP", "html": "&quot;The Kolaghan send them at us. We kill and raise them. They fight the next wave the Kolaghan send. It&#x27;s a neat little cycle.&quot;\n—Asmala, Silumgar <mark>sorcerer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/d/3/d3ab1d6c-09a6-4f6a-9549-94b439a46680.jpg?1782706611"}, {"card": "Arcane Denial", "set": "MSC", "html": "&quot;Your mundane wizardry will not harm the <mark>Sorcerer</mark> Supreme.&quot;\n—Doctor Strange", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/e/5eb843ef-b223-40d0-a461-54b16d188d0e.jpg?1782682544"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Greta, Sweettooth Scourge", "set": "WOE", "html": "{G}, Sacrifice a Food: Put a +1/+1 counter on target creature. Activate only as a <mark>sorcery</mark>."}, {"card": "Pteramander", "set": "OTC", "html": "Flying\n{7}{U}: Adapt 4. This ability costs {1} less to activate for each instant and <mark>sorcery</mark> card in your graveyard. (If this creature has no +1/+1 counters on it, put four +1/+1 counters on it.)"}, {"card": "Ogre Battlecaster", "set": "J22", "html": "Whenever this creature attacks, you may cast target instant or <mark>sorcery</mark> card from your graveyard by paying {R}{R} in addition to its other costs. If that spell would be put into a graveyard, exile it instead. When you cast that spell, this creature gets +X/+0 until end of turn, where X is that spell&#x27;s mana value."}, {"card": "Stormchaser's Talent", "set": "BLB", "html": "(Gain the next level as a <mark>sorcery</mark> to add its ability.)"}, {"card": "Dazzling Sphinx", "set": "OTC", "html": "Whenever this creature deals combat damage to a player, that player exiles cards from the top of their library until they exile an instant or <mark>sorcery</mark> card. You may cast that card without paying its mana cost. Then that player puts the exiled cards that weren&#x27;t cast this way on the bottom of their library in a random order."}, {"card": "Blighted Nightmare", "set": "YECL", "html": "Blight X, Return this enchantment to its owner&#x27;s hand: Return target creature card with mana value X or less from your graveyard to the battlefield. X can&#x27;t be greater than the greatest toughness among creatures you control. Activate only as a <mark>sorcery</mark>."}, {"card": "Sagu Pummeler", "set": "TDM", "html": "Reach\nRenew — {4}{G}, Exile this card from your graveyard: Put two +1/+1 counters and a reach counter on target creature. Activate only as a <mark>sorcery</mark>."}, {"card": "Unscrupulous Contractor", "set": "OTJ", "html": "Plot {2}{B} (You may pay {2}{B} and exile this card from your hand. Cast it as a <mark>sorcery</mark> on a later turn without paying its mana cost. Plot only as a <mark>sorcery</mark>.)"}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/c/2cfd365e-34d1-4224-b925-119000311934.jpg?1782696512", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/2/c/2cfd365e-34d1-4224-b925-119000311934.jpg?1782696512", "card": "Greta, Sweettooth Scourge"}}